    },
    {
      "para_id": "p16",
      "section_id": "s6",
      "section_path": [
        "Addendum 2",
        "Annot. 7 “Secondary monetization methods injected into full-priced products”",
        "Examples"
      ],
      "ordinal": 16,
      "text": "Assassin's Creed Shadows (2025) - video game; the game allows the players to purchase for real money additional premium packs that provide virtual-currency and in-game resources; the in-game resources are required during the game progression, meaning that players are incentivized to purchase to premium packs to skip parts of the game that are boring or are a type of \"grind\"⁶",
